---
import { Image } from "astro:assets";
import Card from "../components/card/Card.astro";
import hikingPic from "../images/Hiking-pic.jpeg";
---

<div class="flex flex-row flex-wrap lg:flex-nowrap gap-24" id="about-me">
  <div
    class="flex flex-col items-center md:items-start lg:basis-2/5 justify-start gap-8 scroll-content opacity-0 translate-y-10 transition-all duration-500"
  >
    <h2 class="text-4xl">Who Am I?</h2>
    <p
      style={{
        fontWeight: "500",
        fontSize: "4rem",
        color: "var(--primary-color)",
        lineHeight: "normal",
      }}
      class="flex flex-wrap items-center text-center md:text-start"
    >
      Occasionally funny, self-claimed creative, and genuinely curious.
    </p>
  </div>
  <div
    class="scroll-content opacity-0 translate-y-10 transition-all duration-500 flex-col flex lg:basis-4/5 gap-4"
  >
    <div class="flex flex-row gap-4 flex-wrap sm:flex-nowrap">
      <Card cardType="secondary" className="flex-1 w-full sm:w-auto">
        <div class="intro flex flex-col gap-4 text-xl">
          <span
            >My name is <span class="underline underline-offset-2"
              >Xiaolei Qin (秦啸雷 if you read Chinese)</span
            >, but you may call me Orion. I am currently a HCI/UX master student
            at UT Austin. I was previously a software engineer who was really
            into design, and now I am learning about it! I care about user
            experience deeply, and I am eager to provide my unique perspectives
            and to become a bridge between engineers and designers!</span
          >
        </div>
      </Card>
      <div class="flex w-full sm:basis-2/5">
        <Card className="flex flex-1">
          <div class="flex flex-col gap-4">
            <p class="flex flex-wrap items-center text-2xl">
              I cook a lot of cuisine from my province.<br />
              I am always out exploring something new with my friends.<br />
            </p>
          </div></Card
        >
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="flex flex-row gap-4 flex-wrap sm:flex-nowrap justify-center">
      <Card className="flex-1 w-full sm:w-auto">
        <div class="flex flex-col gap-4">
          <p class="flex flex-wrap items-center text-2xl">
            I am from Kunming, Yunnan, China.
          </p>
        </div>
      </Card>
      <Image
        class="rounded-2xl m-1 object-cover"
        src={hikingPic}
        alt="I got caught taking a photo"
        width={250}
        quality={100}
      />
      <Card>
        <div class="flex flex-col gap-4">
          <p class="flex flex-wrap items-center text-2xl">
            Traveling is how I learn about the world. I am always planning to travel
            somewhere new, and there are so many views and stories are waiting
            for me to discover.
          </p>
        </div>
      </Card>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>
